'''美克洛嗪'''（英文：Meclizine），中文又称'''氯苯甲嗪'''，是一种用于治疗[[晕动病|晕动病]]、[[头晕|头晕]]和[[眩暈_(醫學)|眩晕]]的[[抗组胺药|抗组胺药]]<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=Meclizine: MedlinePlus Drug Information|url=https://medlineplus.gov/druginfo/meds/a682548.html|accessdate=2021-02-28|work=|publisher=U.S. National Library of Medicine|language=en|archive-date=2021-04-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210422064601/https://medlineplus.gov/druginfo/meds/a682548.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="AHFS2019">{{cite web|title=Meclizine Hydrochloride Monograph for Professionals|url=https://www.drugs.com/monograph/meclizine-hydrochloride.html|publisher=American Society of Health-System Pharmacists|language=en|website=Drugs.com|access-date=22 March 2019|archive-date=2019-12-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191224063905/https://www.drugs.com/monograph/meclizine-hydrochloride.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=氯苯甲嗪|url=http://compling.hss.ntu.edu.sg/ntumc-unipi/cgi-bin/wn-gridx.cgi?gridmode=ntumcgrid&lemma=%E6%B0%AF%E8%8B%AF%E7%94%B2%E5%97%AA&lang=cmn&lang2=eng|accessdate=2021-02-28|work=|publisher=[[南洋理工大学|南洋理工大学]]}}</ref><ref name=":1">{{Cite web|title=美克洛嗪(Meclizine)|url=http://www.hepatox.org/drug/show/333#overview|accessdate=2021-02-28|work=|publisher=www.hepatox.org|language=zh|archive-date=2019-07-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190707093901/http://www.hepatox.org/drug/show/333#overview|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":2">{{Cite web|title=眩晕症治疗的几种常见前庭抑制剂和止吐剂（美克洛嗪）|url=http://bppv.cn/index.php/tag/%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%8B%E6%B4%9B%E5%97%AA/|accessdate=2021-02-28|last=|first=|publisher=头晕和眩晕康复网|language=zh}}</ref>。此药为[[口服给药|口服]]，一般吞服后1小时内开始起效，药效可维持一天<ref name=":0" /><ref name="AHFS2019" /><ref name=":2" />。

美克洛嗪的[[药理学|药理学]]基础与[[抗膽鹼劑|抗胆碱剂]]、[[抗组胺药|抗组胺药]]部分相同，有[[中樞神經系統|中枢神经系统]][[镇静剂|镇静]]、[[局部麻醉药|局部麻醉]]等作用，对内耳迷路（[[骨迷路|骨迷路]]、[[膜迷路|膜迷路]]）以及[[前庭系统|前庭系统]]的活动有抑制作用<ref name="AHFS2019" /><ref name=":2" />。美克洛嗪常见的副作用包括困倦和口干等<ref name=":0" /><ref name="AHFS2019" /><ref name=":1" /><ref name=":2" />。严重可出现视力模糊或[[過敏反應|过敏反应]]<ref name=":0" /><ref name="AHFS2019" />。一般认为孕妇使用较为安全，但还未经过严格详细研究，而[[哺乳期|哺乳期]]使用的安全性未知<ref name="Preg2019">{{cite web|title=Meclizine Use During Pregnancy|url=https://www.drugs.com/pregnancy/meclizine.html|language=en|website=Drugs.com|access-date=3 March 2019|archive-date=2020-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201201031317/https://www.drugs.com/pregnancy/meclizine.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

美克洛嗪于1951年获得[[专利|专利]]，于1953年开始医用<ref name="Fis2006">{{cite book|last1=Fischer|first1=Jnos|last2=Ganellin|first2=C. Robin|name-list-style=vanc|title=Analogue-based Drug Discovery|date=2006|publisher=John Wiley & Sons|isbn=9783527607495|page=547|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=FjKfqkaKkAAC&pg=PA547|language=en|access-date=2021-02-28|archive-date=2021-08-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210829224446/https://books.google.com/books?id=FjKfqkaKkAAC&pg=PA547|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此药一般属于[[通用名药物|通用名药物]]、[[非处方药|非处方药]]<ref name="AHFS2019" /><ref>{{cite book|vauthors=Cappa M, Cianfarani S, Ghizzoni L, Loche S, Maghnie M|title=Advanced Therapies in Pediatric Endocrinology and Diabetology: Workshop, Rome, October 2014|date=2015|publisher=Karger Medical and Scientific Publishers|isbn=9783318056372|page=101|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=myNRCwAAQBAJ&pg=PA101|language=en|access-date=2021-02-28|archive-date=2021-08-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210820112256/https://books.google.com/books?id=myNRCwAAQBAJ&pg=PA101|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2017年，此药是[[美国|美国]]第161位常用药物，有300多万次[[处方|处方]]配药<ref>{{cite web|title=The Top 300 of 2020|url=https://clincalc.com/DrugStats/Top300Drugs.aspx|website=ClinCalc|access-date=11 April 2020|archive-date=2021-02-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210212142534/https://clincalc.com/DrugStats/Top300Drugs.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Meclizine Hydrochloride - Drug Usage Statistics|url=https://clincalc.com/DrugStats/Drugs/MeclizineHydrochloride|website=ClinCalc|access-date=11 April 2020|archive-date=2021-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210226013101/https://clincalc.com/DrugStats/Drugs/MeclizineHydrochloride|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

